    <h3 class="title">
      <a href="https://book.douban.com/review/7909873/" class="title-link">对于历史扫盲，挺有帮助。</a>
      <div class="toggle_review right">        <a href="javascript:;" id="toggle-7909873"class="indicator unfold j" title="展开全文">        </a>
      </div>
    </h3>
    

